Spectral data for Lamps of different colors

Names of datasets containing the wavelengths and tabulated values spectral emittance for the lamps of different types from various suppliers.

uv_lamps

white_lamps

blue_lamps

amber_lamps

red_lamps

Format

A vector of character strings.

See also

lamps.mspct

Examples

uv_lamps
#> [1] "germicidal"      "philips.tl01"    "philips.tl12"    "philips.tl12.mc"
#> [5] "qpanel.uva340"   "qpanel.uvb313"  
blue_lamps
#> [1] "philips.tld36w.18"  "philips.tld.36w.18"
red_lamps
#> [1] "philips.tld36w.15"
amber_lamps
#> [1] "osram.super.vialox"
white_lamps
